1.User enters a task with short description;
	then adds details to the task;
		then adds deadline;
			then assigns the project to the task


2.User wants to edit task
	searches the task by description/project name?									  

3.User wants to reassign the project***???
		searches the old task by description and project name
			user specifies new project name



4. User wants to delete the task
		searches the task by description

5.User wants to mark the task as done



6.User wants to sort tasks by
	project name
	due date

7. User wants to quit and save
